summary.label:
A beautiful music player that manage your songs library in a simple and fast way.

Features:

- tap on the CD to play/stop the track;
- beautiful rotation effect during playback;
- swipe right/left to load the next/previous song;
- look at the lyrics and cover;
- left/right audio VU meters;
- load your favorite playlist;
- manage playback with volume, tracking, shuffle and repeat.
